bilingual.source: The applicant needs to fill out this form.
bilingual.target: 申请人需要填写这份表格。
她是唯一一个符合要求的申请人。

bilingual.source: The applicant was nervous during the interview.
bilingual.target: 申请人在面试时很紧张。

bilingual.source: The applicant filled out the job application form.
bilingual.target: 申请人填写了工作申请表。
每个申请人都必须提供身份证明。

bilingual.source: Each applicant needs to provide two references.
bilingual.target: 每位申请人需要提供两个推荐人。

bilingual.source: The applicant must submit the form by Friday.
bilingual.target: 申请人必须在星期五之前提交表格。

bilingual.source: The applicant was found ineligible for the scholarship.
bilingual.target: 申请人被发现不合格获得奖学金。

bilingual.source: We need to know the applicant's educational background.
bilingual.target: 我们需要了解申请人的教育背景。

bilingual.source: The interviewer is assessing each applicant's qualifications.
bilingual.target: 面试官正在评估每位申请人的资格。

yingyinNormal.en: "Dear applicant Boing." It doesn't say that. "This year we are only accepting married applicants." It doesn't say that! "So we regret to inform you that..." Regret to inform me?
yingyinNormal.zh: “亲爱的申请人蹦蹦。”不是这么说的。“今年我们只接收已婚的申请人。”上面不是这么说的！“因此，我们遗憾地通知你……”遗憾地通知我？

direction_info.description:
数据源自2012-2023年12年间全国考研试卷，由搜狗翻译进行大数据分析汇总，数据仅供参考。

<highlight> 考频分布</highlight>
由搜狗翻译收集历年真题试卷、汇总单词出现的总频次、释义分布。题型选自2012-2023年全国考研英语一和考研英语二共24套考研试卷，包括阅读、完型填空、翻译、写作等所有题型。

<highlight> 考纲释义</highlight>
精选全国考研考纲词汇、单词义项，由搜狗大数据与考纲、历年真题进行匹配。

<highlight>真题例句</highlight>
精选2012-2023年12年间全国考研英语一和考研英语二试卷，由搜狗大数据与搜索内容匹配历年真题例句。

搜狗翻译拥有最终解释权。

derivative_info_list.mean: n. 申请；应用；涂抹于表面；敷用；持续的努力；艰苦的工作；应用程序；应用软件；关联；实际运用

sense_info_list.en: a person who formally requests something, especially a job, or to study at a college or university

examination_example.sentence: Attempts have been made to curb this tendency, for example, by trying to incorporate some measure of quality as well as quantity into the assessment of an <highlight>applicant</highlight>'s papers.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 已经有很多尝试被用来遏制这种趋势，比如:通过将对质量以及数量的衡量标准纳入到对申请者论文的评估中。

examination_example.sentence: If we know female job screeners are more likely to reject attractive female <highlight>applicants</highlight>, we can hire outside screeners.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 如果我们知道女性工作筛选者更有可能拒绝有吸引力的女性申请人，我们可以雇佣外部筛选者。

examination_example.sentence: The interviewers had rated <highlight>applicants</highlight> on a scale of one to five.
examination_example.sentence_trans: 面试官对应聘者用1到5分的分数进行评级。
